and to see

00:01:57.384 --> 00:01:58.652 align:middle line:84%
if there's something
much more to us

00:01:58.652 --> 00:02:01.889 align:middle line:84%
than what meets the eye,
the material frame.

00:02:01.889 --> 00:02:04.558 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: And where do you
think, because you speak

00:02:04.558 --> 00:02:06.961 align:middle line:84%
