00:02:06.961 --> 00:02:08.629 align:middle line:90%
where do you think they're at

00:02:08.629 --> 00:02:10.564 align:middle line:84%
and where is society
at with that?

00:02:10.564 --> 00:02:11.966 align:middle line:84%
>> Lakhani: The world is
very interesting now, you see,

00:02:11.966 --> 00:02:14.401 align:middle line:84%
because we sometimes feel
the modern society has

00:02:14.401 --> 00:02:16.270 align:middle line:84%
forgotten religions and
they're going to become

00:02:16.270 --> 00:02:17.571 align:middle line:90%
and they're lost in the way.

00:02:17.571 --> 00:02:19.073 align:middle line:90%
It's nothing of the sort.

00:02:19.073 --> 00:02:22.543 align:middle line:84%
Humanity continues to
evolve and evolve at a pace

00:02:22.543 --> 00:02:24.345 align:middle line:90%
that suits his own requirement.

00:02:24.345 --> 00:02:27.047 align:middle line:84%
What I find with the modern
youth is a very refreshing

00:02:27.047 --> 00:02:29.683 align:middle line:84%
approach to what religions
were all about in the past,

00:02:29.683 --> 00:02:31.585 align:middle line:84%
and so they are trying
to re-explore

00:02:31.585 --> 00:02:34.054 align:middle line:84%
or rediscover the spiritual
underpinning

00:02:34.054 --> 00:02:37.391 align:middle line:84%
without using a prescriptive
religion. So this is a reality.

00:02:37.391 --> 00:02:40.127 align:middle line:84%
When I go to schools, I do lots
of assemblies. I must have gone

00:02:40.127 --> 00:02:43.364 align:middle line:84%
