with this enterprise?

00:02:55.409 --> 00:02:59.346 align:middle line:84%
What I am finding surprisingly
and perhaps very interestingly

00:02:59.346 --> 00:03:03.517 align:middle line:84%
is that sometimes 90% of these
youngsters who are thinking

00:03:03.517 --> 00:03:06.820 align:middle line:84%
for themselves now very
happily put their hands

00:03:06.820 --> 00:03:08.856 align:middle line:84%
up as being agnostic,
