00:27:48.567 --> 00:27:53.339 align:middle line:84%
In the material world, the
buzzing that you see is, if you

00:27:53.339 --> 00:27:57.810 align:middle line:84%
like, spirit percolating,
coming through more clearly,

00:27:57.810 --> 00:28:00.846 align:middle line:84%
and humanity is the best
expression of the spirit.

00:28:00.846 --> 00:28:03.783 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: At the same
time our body dissolve

00:28:03.783 --> 00:28:05.751 align:middle line:84%
and we're here only
a certain time

00:28:05.751 --> 00:28:09.255 align:middle line:90%
and so where is this really?

00:28:09.255 --> 00:28:12.291 align:middle line:84%
We stress and we have
emotions and all of this.

00:28:12.291 --> 00:28:14.326 align:middle line:90%
So, where do we look at?

00:28:14.326 --> 00:28:15.995 align:middle line:84%
>> Lakhani: We look
at many places.

00:28:15.995 --> 00:28:19.799 align:middle line:84%
For example, the India tradition
means Hinduism, Buddhism,

00:28:19.799 --> 00:28:20.900 align:middle line:90%
Chinese, some say

00:28:20.900 --> 00:28:23.436 align:middle line:84%
your journey doesn't
stop when the body dies.

00:28:23.436 --> 00:28:27.440 align:middle line:84%
Death is seen as a comma and not
a full stop in the tradition.

00:28:27.440 --> 00:28:30.376 align:middle line:84%
So if you say what happens when
the body dies and you dissolve

00:28:30.376 --> 00:28:31.911 align:middle line:84%
and your body, you dissolve it
or you burn it, what happens?

00:28:31.911 --> 00:28:34.947 align:middle line:84%
Well, the thing that is
underpinning has not lost

00:28:34.947 --> 00:28:37.316 align:middle line:90%
its journey.

00:28:37.316 --> 00:28:41.821 align:middle line:84%
It continues the journey, it
manifests itself in another body

00:28:41.821 --> 00:28:44.557 align:middle line:84%
until it discovers what you
said why does it continue

00:28:44.557 --> 00:28:45.858 align:middle line:90%
to be reborn?

00:28:45.858 --> 00:28:47.726 align:middle line:90%
Why does it bother?

00:28:47.726 --> 00:28:48.494 align:middle line:90%
You've got the drives.

00:28:48.494 --> 00:28:49.895 align:middle line:90%
Now, again, when you want

00:28:49.895 --> 00:28:52.298 align:middle line:84%
suss out the human condition,
it's not only the physical world

00:28:52.298 --> 00:28:54.567 align:middle line:84%
that you look at but
you look at inner man.

00:28:54.567 --> 00:28:59.672 align:middle line:84%
Now, we all have lots of drives,
lots of emotions and we see

00:28:59.672 --> 00:29:04.310 align:middle line:84%
if you like appear to be kind
of, you know, unfulfillable,

00:29:04.310 --> 00:29:07.346 align:middle line:84%
difficult to fulfill and
a continuous struggle

00:29:07.346 --> 00:29:08.681 align:middle line:90%
to find expression

00:29:08.681 --> 00:29:11.584 align:middle line:84%
or to resolve our human
condition or fulfill desires.

00:29:11.584 --> 00:29:14.453 align:middle line:84%
Now, this is if you like the
reason why we continue the

00:29:14.453 --> 00:29:16.355 align:middle line:90%
journey of reincarnation.

00:29:16.355 --> 00:29:19.925 align:middle line:84%
The thing that is trying to
get fulfillment struggles

00:29:19.925 --> 00:29:22.294 align:middle line:84%
in one lifetime so it
tries to get fulfillment

00:29:22.294 --> 00:29:25.397 align:middle line:84%
in the second life or the next
life and carries on the journey

00:29:25.397 --> 00:29:28.100 align:middle line:84%
and the only way this
fulfillment comes

00:29:28.100 --> 00:29:31.770 align:middle line:84%
and the reason this will
continue, the only resolution

00:29:31.770 --> 00:29:33.439 align:middle line:90%
of this human dilemma is

00:29:33.439 --> 00:29:38.210 align:middle line:84%
when the individual rediscovers
its essential nature, not

00:29:38.210 --> 00:29:41.480 align:middle line:84%
as a material being chasing
after material objectives

00:29:41.480 --> 00:29:42.982 align:middle line:90%
but a spiritual being.

00:29:42.982 --> 00:29:46.685 align:middle line:84%
So once it discovers that I am
the spirit. Again, this is

00:29:46.685 --> 00:29:48.854 align:middle line:90%
experiential, not

00:29:48.854 --> 00:29:50.055 align:middle line:84%
intellectual. "Oh, I believe
that!" doesn't help you.

00:29:50.055 --> 00:29:51.624 align:middle line:84%
Your desires are still going
to come and bother you.

00:29:51.624 --> 00:29:54.326 align:middle line:84%
So when you experience that you
are the spirit, you are full

00:29:54.326 --> 00:29:57.029 align:middle line:84%
and resplendent, there's
nothing missing in you,

00:29:57.029 --> 00:30:00.432 align:middle line:84%
then desires fall away, then
no more reincarnation.

00:30:00.432 --> 00:30:04.270 align:middle line:84%
So then the human condition
has been resolved permanently

00:30:04.270 --> 00:30:06.906 align:middle line:84%
because then you say
I am full. What desires?

00:30:06.906 --> 00:30:09.875 align:middle line:84%
I don't have to fight desires.
They don't bother me anymore.

00:30:09.875 --> 00:30:10.709 align:middle line:90%
They fall off.

00:30:10.709 --> 00:30:12.211 align:middle line:90%
If you look at every prophet,

00:30:12.211 --> 00:30:14.079 align:middle line:84%
this is what happens
in the lives.

00:30:14.079 --> 00:30:15.581 align:middle line:90%
You see desires drop off.

00:30:15.581 --> 00:30:18.584 align:middle line:84%
It's not better to fight it and
bottle it up.

00:30:18.584 --> 00:30:20.386 align:middle line:84%
They just disappear.
They just fizzle away.

00:30:20.386 --> 00:30:24.623 align:middle line:84%
They discover their real nature
in the spirit so the resolution

00:30:24.623 --> 00:30:26.592 align:middle line:90%
of the human condition is not

00:30:26.592 --> 00:30:28.827 align:middle line:84%
in the material level
it's a spiritual level

00:30:28.827 --> 00:30:32.898 align:middle line:84%
to rediscover our identity
as spirit, and once you do

00:30:32.898 --> 00:30:35.768 align:middle line:84%
that, the journey comes
to a halt in a nice manner.

00:30:35.768 --> 00:30:38.971 align:middle line:84%
It's not that you, you know,
lose your individuality.

00:30:38.971 --> 00:30:41.674 align:middle line:84%
You discover your individuality,
you are the spirit,

00:30:41.674 --> 00:30:43.275 align:middle line:90%
my friend, you are that.

00:30:43.275 --> 00:30:45.244 align:middle line:84%
That's what humanity
is studying up to do.

00:30:45.244 --> 00:30:47.279 align:middle line:84%
It does it through its
various methods of trying

00:30:47.279 --> 00:30:51.050 align:middle line:84%
to fulfill wishes, trying to
chase after pleasurable things.

00:30:51.050 --> 00:30:52.051 align:middle line:84%
So, all these hedonistic
pursuits

00:30:52.051 --> 00:30:53.686 align:middle line:84%
that we see are not to be
villified.

00:30:53.686 --> 00:30:56.922 align:middle line:84%
We are trying to find
expression of fulfillment

00:30:56.922 --> 00:30:58.290 align:middle line:90%
through this hedonistic journey.

00:30:58.290 --> 00:30:59.758 align:middle line:90%
I like pleasurable things.

00:30:59.758 --> 00:31:02.261 align:middle line:90%
Why not? No, why? Really, why?

00:31:02.261 --> 00:31:03.696 align:middle line:90%
This is his journey.

00:31:03.696 --> 00:31:05.264 align:middle line:84%
It's only when it gets whacked
left and right

00:31:05.264 --> 00:31:06.865 align:middle line:84%
and suddenly something is wrong
here.

00:31:06.865 --> 00:31:07.666 align:middle line:90%
Then he says something...

00:31:07.666 --> 00:31:08.867 align:middle line:90%
I need to find a better way.

00:31:08.867 --> 00:31:10.736 align:middle line:84%
So you say, oh, I must
chase after this objective

00:31:10.736 --> 00:31:12.404 align:middle line:84%
or that objective and
you get that objective

00:31:12.404 --> 00:31:14.006 align:middle line:90%
and three more desires arise.

00:31:14.006 --> 00:31:15.341 align:middle line:90%
So where do they come from?

00:31:15.341 --> 00:31:17.309 align:middle line:84%
You fulfill them and three
more arise, thirty more arise

00:31:17.309 --> 00:31:19.011 align:middle line:84%
and you say this is
getting out of hand.

00:31:19.011 --> 00:31:21.413 align:middle line:84%
So when the maturity arises
something is wrong here,

00:31:21.413 --> 00:31:23.816 align:middle line:84%
we've been chasing
after shadows.

00:31:23.816 --> 00:31:25.684 align:middle line:84%
When the maturity
comes naturally,

00:31:25.684 --> 00:31:27.853 align:middle line:84%
it's not by a guru saying
oh, don't do this,

00:31:27.853 --> 00:31:29.622 align:middle line:90%
Stop your desire! It won't work.

00:31:29.622 --> 00:31:31.023 align:middle line:90%
When the maturity comes

00:31:31.023 --> 00:31:33.892 align:middle line:84%
from within. I know something is
seriously wrong here I've been

00:31:33.892 --> 00:31:37.196 align:middle line:84%
chasing and biting at shadows,
and I'm not getting fulfilled.

00:31:37.196 --> 00:31:37.997 align:middle line:90%
So what is the reason?

00:31:37.997 --> 00:31:39.798 align:middle line:90%
When that starting up comes,

00:31:39.798 --> 00:31:42.401 align:middle line:84%
then you become truly
interested in spiritualty.

00:31:42.401 --> 00:31:43.736 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise you're
just tokenistic.

00:31:43.736 --> 00:31:45.137 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Yeah, yeah.

00:31:45.137 --> 00:31:47.239 align:middle line:84%
It feels like once
there's this recognition

00:31:47.239 --> 00:31:49.375 align:middle line:90%
that we are spirit then related

00:31:49.375 --> 00:31:53.178 align:middle line:84%
to this time/space conversation
then it's not even a

00:31:53.178 --> 00:31:54.480 align:middle line:90%
conversation anymore.

00:31:54.480 --> 00:31:57.549 align:middle line:84%
>> Lakhani: Space
and time again follow

00:31:57.549 --> 00:32:00.552 align:middle line:84%
because the spirit is not
something that is singular

00:32:00.552 --> 00:32:03.222 align:middle line:84%
or plural, it's not in
this part of the location

00:32:03.222 --> 00:32:05.557 align:middle line:84%
because people say Mr. Lakhani,
if we are spirit,

00:32:05.557 --> 00:32:06.825 align:middle line:84%
which part of the
universe are we?

00:32:06.825 --> 00:32:09.328 align:middle line:84%
I said don't you see the
university is in you, not you,

00:32:09.328 --> 00:32:11.230 align:middle line:84%
so you don't find
yourself here or there.

00:32:11.230 --> 00:32:15.467 align:middle line:84%
If you believe in this idea
of spirit, it underpins all

00:32:15.467 --> 00:32:19.505 align:middle line:84%
of reality, all of space,
all of time, whole cosmos.

00:32:19.505 --> 00:32:21.707 align:middle line:84%
If you are underpinning,
you can't say where am I?

00:32:21.707 --> 00:32:23.676 align:middle line:84%
You are everywhere
and nowhere really.

00:32:23.676 --> 00:32:26.011 align:middle line:84%
You aren't in any
individual object and

00:32:26.011 --> 00:32:28.080 align:middle line:84%
yet you underpin the
whole of this creation.

00:32:28.080 --> 00:32:31.216 align:middle line:84%
Again, it sounds very nice
and artistic and, you know,

00:32:31.216 --> 00:32:33.585 align:middle line:84%
poetic, but really
what I'm saying is you need

00:32:33.585 --> 00:32:34.987 align:middle line:90%
to experience it.

00:32:34.987 --> 00:32:37.089 align:middle line:90%
Look at the lives of prophets.

00:32:37.089 --> 00:32:39.224 align:middle line:84%
They live as if they
own the whole universe

00:32:39.224 --> 00:32:41.126 align:middle line:90%
and desire nothing from it.

00:32:41.126 --> 00:32:43.128 align:middle line:90%
This is the sign of a prophett.

00:32:43.128 --> 00:32:45.364 align:middle line:84%
They seem..they walk about with
the majest

00:32:45.364 --> 00:32:48.367 align:middle line:84%
of a real master
of the universe and

00:32:48.367 --> 00:32:51.737 align:middle line:84%
yet there are not desires of
any aspect of this master.

00:32:51.737 --> 00:32:53.339 align:middle line:90%
They don't own this or that.

00:32:53.339 --> 00:32:56.241 align:middle line:84%
They walk like real masters
otherwise they become slaves.

00:32:56.241 --> 00:32:59.778 align:middle line:84%
If desires infect them,
they're no better than us.

00:32:59.778 --> 00:33:03.015 align:middle line:84%
The desires drop off and they
live a very masterful life.

00:33:03.015 --> 00:33:04.249 align:middle line:90%
Look at their lives.

00:33:04.249 --> 00:33:06.051 align:middle line:84%
If that doesn't charge you up,
nothing else will.

00:33:06.051 --> 00:33:07.319 align:middle line:84%
People say should I be
studying philosophy?

00:33:07.319 --> 00:33:11.690 align:middle line:84%
No, no, I said study the
lives of recent personalities

00:33:11.690 --> 00:33:14.426 align:middle line:84%
that attract you who are
spiritually oriented.

00:33:14.426 --> 00:33:17.396 align:middle line:84%
Just look at their lives,
this is very personal,

00:33:17.396 --> 00:33:19.898 align:middle line:84%
very anthropocentric so you're
looking at human condition

00:33:19.898 --> 00:33:22.134 align:middle line:84%
and human resolution
and look at the lives.

00:33:22.134 --> 00:33:24.002 align:middle line:84%
See if it doesn't capture
you, nothing else will.

00:33:24.002 --> 00:33:25.437 align:middle line:90%
Philosophy comes afterwards.

00:33:25.437 --> 00:33:29.241 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: The oneness, a lot of
people speak of this oneness,

00:33:29.241 --> 00:33:32.911 align:middle line:84%
do you think this is something
that's related to coming back

00:33:32.911 --> 00:33:35.147 align:middle line:84%
to our spirit, right,
and to understand

00:33:35.147 --> 00:33:39.618 align:middle line:90%
that we are all interconnected?

00:33:39.618 --> 00:33:42.087 align:middle line:84%
>> Lakhani: Again, the
spirit is never plural,

00:33:42.087 --> 00:33:43.389 align:middle line:90%
it is always singular.

00:33:43.389 --> 00:33:45.791 align:middle line:84%
It's not that my spirit is
different from your spirit.

00:33:45.791 --> 00:33:48.427 align:middle line:84%
The thing that is looking out
through my eyes and bubbling

00:33:48.427 --> 00:33:50.863 align:middle line:84%
up through this particular
frame is also bubbling

00:33:50.863 --> 00:33:52.531 align:middle line:84%
out through that
particular frame.

00:33:52.531 --> 00:33:56.368 align:middle line:84%
So the link that I have with
other humanity, it's not

00:33:56.368 --> 00:33:59.338 align:middle line:84%
at the material level as Dawkins
would suggest but at the deeper,

00:33:59.338 --> 00:34:01.640 align:middle line:84%
spiritual level we
are linked up.

00:34:01.640 --> 00:34:02.740 align:middle line:90%
So that is why, you know,

00:34:02.740 --> 00:34:05.177 align:middle line:84%
this is again a very
interesting litmus test.

00:34:05.177 --> 00:34:07.412 align:middle line:84%
The reason why all the prophets
were in love with humanity is

00:34:07.412 --> 00:34:09.782 align:middle line:84%
because they were... actually
experienced that oneness

00:34:09.782 --> 00:34:11.383 align:middle line:90%
with the rest of humanity.

00:34:11.383 --> 00:34:13.117 align:middle line:90%
They see themselves reflected

00:34:13.117 --> 00:34:14.952 align:middle line:84%
in other human beings
so they are stuck.

00:34:14.952 --> 00:34:16.789 align:middle line:90%
You see they want to express.

00:34:16.789 --> 00:34:20.025 align:middle line:84%
So the same is true with this
oneness is something, again,

00:34:20.025 --> 00:34:24.430 align:middle line:84%
if you look at some of the
modern mystic poets they will

00:34:24.430 --> 00:34:26.164 align:middle line:84%
talk about the same thing
without the tops and turns

00:34:26.164 --> 00:34:29.068 align:middle line:84%
of religion. They will
say a great peace seems

00:34:29.068 --> 00:34:30.202 align:middle line:90%
to descend on us.

00:34:30.202 --> 00:34:32.905 align:middle line:84%
We seem to be one with
the whole of creation.

00:34:32.905 --> 00:34:35.140 align:middle line:84%
This is a sign of a
spiritual experience.

00:34:35.140 --> 00:34:36.642 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: Like Rumi, who was
great.

00:34:36.642 --> 00:34:39.244 align:middle line:84%
>> Lakhani: Rumi or lots of
other, you know, William Blake,

00:34:39.244 --> 00:34:41.847 align:middle line:84%
a lot of them when they talk of
this Wadsworth, when they talk

00:34:41.847 --> 00:34:43.816 align:middle line:84%
of this oneness, you can
feel they're feeling it

00:34:43.816 --> 00:34:45.651 align:middle line:90%
with whole of creation.

00:34:45.651 --> 00:34:47.952 align:middle line:84%
When you see that
visible in their poetry

00:34:47.952 --> 00:34:52.024 align:middle line:84%
or in the literature, when you
read it, it gives you a thrill

00:34:52.024 --> 00:34:53.959 align:middle line:84%
because some of that thing
is passed on to you

00:34:53.959 --> 00:34:55.694 align:middle line:84%
through that particular
vocabulary.

00:34:55.694 --> 00:34:57.863 align:middle line:84%
So in a way, this
oneness is something.

00:34:57.863 --> 00:34:59.932 align:middle line:84%
Again, the only way
you'll overcome, you know,

00:34:59.932 --> 00:35:02.468 align:middle line:84%
we were talking about earlier
about fear is when you say

00:35:02.468 --> 00:35:05.037 align:middle line:84%
that I am one with whole
creation how can you be fearful

00:35:05.037 --> 00:35:05.871 align:middle line:90%
of anything?

00:35:05.871 --> 00:35:07.940 align:middle line:90%
It's you alone with everything.

00:35:07.940 --> 00:35:11.243 align:middle line:84%
So, fear that is natural kind
of thing that you possess

00:35:11.243 --> 00:35:15.414 align:middle line:84%
from the animal kingdom that in
faction we have fear it will

00:35:15.414 --> 00:35:16.748 align:middle line:90%
drop off as well.

00:35:16.748 --> 00:35:18.750 align:middle line:90%
Fear? What fear?

00:35:18.750 --> 00:35:21.487 align:middle line:84%
So discovering the oneness
is the only way you overcome

00:35:21.487 --> 00:35:22.621 align:middle line:90%
fear forever.

00:35:22.621 --> 00:35:25.457 align:middle line:84%
This is, again, it's not
just a negative thing

00:35:25.457 --> 00:35:26.792 align:middle line:90%
that you work on fear.

00:35:26.792 --> 00:35:30.796 align:middle line:84%
It's a very positive, very
exciting experiential dimension

00:35:30.796 --> 00:35:33.632 align:middle line:84%
because you can say, oh,
close my eyes and meditate.

00:35:33.632 --> 00:35:35.734 align:middle line:84%
That's a very limited
way of meditating.

00:35:35.734 --> 00:35:37.736 align:middle line:90%
Meditate with open eyes.

00:35:37.736 --> 00:35:40.506 align:middle line:84%
With open eyes look around
and see your link with all

00:35:40.506 --> 00:35:43.408 align:middle line:84%
of creations especially with
human beings who light up.

00:35:43.408 --> 00:35:47.546 align:middle line:84%
This is becoming one of
meditating with open eyes.

00:35:47.546 --> 00:35:51.083 align:middle line:84%
Why not? This is what my mentor
Vivekananda used to do.

00:35:51.083 --> 00:35:53.585 align:middle line:84%
You see when he talks,
he talks with the spirit.

00:35:53.585 --> 00:35:56.822 align:middle line:84%
Anybody that comes near him
is, of course, charged up.

00:35:56.822 --> 00:35:57.890 align:middle line:90%
Also with Raman Maharshi.

00:35:57.890 --> 00:35:59.525 align:middle line:84%
When Brunton used to visit Raman
Maharshi,

00:35:59.525 --> 00:36:02.060 align:middle line:84%
he would say sometimes Raman
Maharshi wouldn't speak at all.

00:36:02.060 --> 00:36:04.196 align:middle line:84%
He'll just look at
you and his glance

00:36:04.196 --> 00:36:06.865 align:middle line:84%
at you would really lift you
off that I'm no longer the body,

00:36:06.865 --> 00:36:08.500 align:middle line:84%
I am the spirit of--
Oh, chaps,

00:36:08.500 --> 00:36:09.735 align:middle line:90%
I feel I'm floating.

00:36:09.735 --> 00:36:13.338 align:middle line:84%
These are the real experience
of real genuine prophets

00:36:13.338 --> 00:36:15.440 align:middle line:84%
who are not only
talking about oneness

00:36:15.440 --> 00:36:16.842 align:middle line:90%
who are experiencing oneness.

00:36:16.842 --> 00:36:19.878 align:middle line:84%
If you come in front of them,
you experience the same oneness.

00:36:19.878 --> 00:36:23.181 align:middle line:84%
It lifts you off, your very
limited vision regarding

00:36:23.181 --> 00:36:24.550 align:middle line:90%
who you think you are,

00:36:24.550 --> 00:36:28.186 align:middle line:84%
suddenly from the very limited
vision, that dream is broken

00:36:28.186 --> 00:36:30.522 align:middle line:84%
and you see oneness
with greater creation.

00:36:30.522 --> 00:36:34.293 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: Yeah, does that
shadow or that darker side

00:36:34.293 --> 00:36:38.030 align:middle line:84%
